Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:03.76,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.89,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Přišla tvá máma!
